## 角色

- id: {{ perspective.actor.id }}
- 姓名: {{ perspective.actor.name }}
- 描述: {{ perspective.actor.description }}
- 公开状态: {{ perspective.actor.public_state }}
- 私有状态: {{ perspective.actor.private_state }}
- 当前活动: {{ perspective.actor.current_activity.name }}

## 触发回应的用户输入

{{ perspective.user_input }}

## 地点

- id: {{ perspective.location.id }}
- 名称: {{ perspective.location.name }}
- 描述: {{ perspective.location.description }}

## 相关持有物

{% for entry in perspective.inventory %}
- stack id: {{ entry.stack_id }}; item id: {{ entry.item_id }}; {{ entry.name }} x{{ entry.quantity }}; 描述: {{ entry.description }}{% if entry.quality %}; quality: {{ entry.quality }}{% endif %}
{% else %}
- 无
{% endfor %}

## 可感知角色

{% for entry in perspective.perceived_characters %}
- id: {{ entry.character.id }}; 姓名: {{ entry.character.name }}; 状态: {{ entry.character.public_state }}; affordances: {{ entry.affordances }}{% if entry.notes %}; notes: {{ entry.notes }}{% endif %}
{% else %}
- 无
{% endfor %}

## 回忆

{% for entry in perspective.relevant_memories %}
- memory id: {{ entry.memory.id }}; 摘要: {{ entry.memory.summary }}; event: {{ entry.event_name }}; support: {{ entry.support_type }}; confidence: {{ entry.confidence }}; stance: {{ entry.stance }}
{% else %}
- 无
{% endfor %}

## 原始 ActionProposal

{{ proposal }}

## 不完整的 speak action

- label: {{ action.label }}
- target ids: {{ action.target_ids }}
- expected effects: {{ action.expected_effects }}
- required preconditions: {{ action.required_preconditions }}

## 提案理由

{{ reasoning_summary }}

## 建议记忆更新

{% for update in memory_updates_suggested %}
- {{ update }}
{% else %}
- 无
{% endfor %}

只返回台词文本。
